Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.86,0:00:10.61,somari text,,0,0,0,,別哭啦 奇奇拉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.73,0:00:12.65,somari text,,0,0,0,,這樣眼淚會哭乾的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.57,0:00:16.56,somari text,,0,0,0,,索瑪麗  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.07,0:00:18.91,somari text,,0,0,0,,索瑪麗  該上馬車了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.54,0:00:20.34,somari text,,0,0,0,,差不多得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.80,0:00:21.25,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.54,0:00:24.16,somari text,,0,0,0,,沒事的  奇奇拉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.66,0:00:29.21,somari text,,0,0,0,,我和爸爸約好了  要永遠一起旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.05,0:00:31.63,somari text,,0,0,0,,所以我一定會再回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.92,0:00:32.26,somari text,,0,0,0,,好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.26,0:00:36.18,somari text,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.89,0:00:46.31,somari text,,0,0,0,,小姑娘想和你一直在一起的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.44,0:00:49.48,somari text,,0,0,0,,希望你不要辜負
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.28,0:00:57.03,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.03,0:00:59.37,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了  索瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.29,0:01:02.87,somari text,,0,0,0,,走吧  要出發了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.62,0:01:06.55,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯  也是
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,----op----
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.06,0:01:34.81,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}何なんだろう　この胸のモヤモヤは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.06,0:01:34.81,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}心中的這份躁動  是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.11,0:01:42.57,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}洗いたてのタオルに顔を埋めるような
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.11,0:01:42.57,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}就像將臉埋入剛洗過的毛巾一般
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.24,0:01:49.70,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}鳥が鳴いている　朝焼けのメロディー
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.24,0:01:49.70,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}鳥兒們吟唱著  朝霞的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.01,0:02:00.76,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}どこまで歩いても　この道は続いている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.01,0:02:00.76,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}無論走到哪  這道路都會延伸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.81,0:02:09.86,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}手を繋ぐよりも　指を繋ぐような
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.81,0:02:09.86,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}比起手牽手  更像是緊握這手指
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.00,0:02:16.63,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}寒い夜は寄り添い合って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.00,0:02:16.63,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}寒冷的夜晚彼此相依
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.16,0:02:21.99,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}星空の毛布で眠る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.16,0:02:21.99,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}以星空為毯子安眠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.72,0:02:27.23,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}テーブルの向こうの笑顔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.72,0:02:27.23,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}餐桌對面的笑臉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.77,0:02:35.67,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}最果ての地を君と目指した
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.77,0:02:35.67,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}為你指向盡頭之地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.94,0:02:45.18,somari op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}ありがとうはこっちの言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.94,0:02:45.18,somari op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}我才該說謝謝你才對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:08.66,somari title,,0,0,0,,{\fade(1000,850)\blur6\pos(1628,1061.6)}躊躇的鳥兒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.49,0:03:00.99,somari text,,0,0,0,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:03.87,somari text,,0,0,0,,坐馬車很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:06.74,somari text,,0,0,0,,可是太熱了一點也不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.87,0:03:15.44,somari text,,0,0,0,,日落了會有沙塵暴  要趁現在移動才行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.43,0:03:18.70,somari text,,0,0,0,,在到達村子前稍微忍耐一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.02,0:03:21.43,somari text,,0,0,0,,喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.50,0:03:24.85,somari text,,0,0,0,,缺少水份補給很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.69,0:03:28.89,somari text,,0,0,0,,是溫的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:31.89,somari text,,0,0,0,,到達後  首先要休息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:34.98,somari text,,0,0,0,,我想喝冰的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.22,0:03:41.70,somari text,,0,0,0,,活過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.65,0:03:44.78,somari text,,0,0,0,,你的表現還是那麼誇張
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:46.25,somari text,,0,0,0,,要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:47.37,somari text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.46,0:03:59.90,somari text,,0,0,0,,這地方好奇怪啊  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:04.31,somari text,,0,0,0,,這座「酒杯村」是在火山口遺蹟上建造的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:06.44,somari text,,0,0,0,,旅行者們的停宿之處
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.41,0:04:11.06,somari text,,0,0,0,,因為這裡的地形最適合等待沙塵暴離去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:13.56,somari text,,0,0,0,,所以旅行者們自然會聚集在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:15.40,somari text,,0,0,0,,因而變成了村子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.88,0:04:23.49,somari text,,0,0,0,,索瑪麗想吃這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.11,0:04:26.62,somari text,,0,0,0,,光吃冷的食物身體會著涼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:27.99,somari text,,0,0,0,,否決
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:31.20,somari text,,0,0,0,,可是一直都好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:32.95,somari text,,0,0,0,,是旅行者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:38.17,somari text,,0,0,0,,請  祝旅行愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.34,0:04:42.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,喂  這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:45.01,somari text,,0,0,0,,是村子長久以來的習俗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.60,0:04:47.26,somari text,,0,0,0,,根據以前的傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.09,0:04:49.85,somari text,,0,0,0,,在這裡成為村子之前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.47,0:04:53.52,somari text,,0,0,0,,在火山遺蹟裡聚集了幾位旅行者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:57.31,somari text,,0,0,0,,他們中有一個擅長喝酒的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:05:01.41,somari text,,0,0,0,,他把他的酒分給大家  舉辦了宴會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.32,0:05:08.74,somari text,,0,0,0,,然後不可思議的是  這些旅行者們全員安全地穿過了沙漠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:12.99,somari text,,0,0,0,,從那以後  這座村子就會請旅行者喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.18,0:05:15.37,somari text,,0,0,0,,以此來祈願平安穿越沙漠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.20,0:05:18.20,somari text,,0,0,0,,畢竟這裡經常會有被稱為「龍之旋風」的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:22.34,somari text,,0,0,0,,危險的龍捲風發生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.00,0:05:23.67,somari text,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:28.13,somari text,,0,0,0,,那是以村子名產玉米發酵蒸餾出的酒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:29.72,somari text,,0,0,0,,玉米？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:32.89,somari text,,0,0,0,,好像是砂糖的原料吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:34.68,somari text,,0,0,0,,那個甜甜的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:37.31,somari text,,0,0,0,,索瑪麗還不能喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:38.14,somari text,,0,0,0,,好殘忍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.81,0:05:42.32,somari text,,0,0,0,,小朋友也有玉米冰淇淋吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.57,0:05:43.44,somari text,,0,0,0,,冰淇淋！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.19,0:05:46.86,somari text,,0,0,0,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.65,0:05:48.07,somari text,,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:50.74,somari text,,0,0,0,,那個玉米冰淇淋能給我一個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:55.87,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.37,0:05:57.87,somari text,,0,0,0,,學我點冰淇淋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.45,0:06:00.13,somari text,,0,0,0,,我又沒學你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:02.09,somari text,,0,0,0,,那個不好意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:04.93,somari text,,0,0,0,,冰淇淋就剩下一人份的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.93,0:06:07.05,somari text,,0,0,0,,我要  索瑪麗要吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:10.01,somari text,,0,0,0,,等下  你幹嘛偷跑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:11.35,somari text,,0,0,0,,先到先得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.38,0:06:15.77,somari text,,0,0,0,,不是應該讓給年長者嗎  你個小不點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:16.73,somari text,,0,0,0,,我才不是小不點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:18.48,somari text,,0,0,0,,你才是一點大人樣都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:20.98,somari text - top,,0,0,0,,{\an7}讓給我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.23,0:06:20.07,somari text - top,,0,0,0,,{\an9}才不給
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.07,0:06:21.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,索瑪麗  在店裡要安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.33,0:06:23.52,somari text,,0,0,0,,區區一個小不點這麼囂張…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:27.64,somari text,,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.57,0:06:30.36,somari text,,0,0,0,,你在做什麼  烏佐伊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:31.74,somari text,,0,0,0,,海特拉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.62,0:06:38.25,somari text,,0,0,0,,我的同伴給您添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:43.40,somari text,,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:45.67,somari text,,0,0,0,,那很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.25,0:06:47.80,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯  碰到困難了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.21,0:06:53.19,somari text,,0,0,0,,長途旅行的話  還是準備一輛馬車比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.76,0:06:54.47,somari text,,0,0,0,,很好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:06:58.81,somari text,,0,0,0,,讓給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:01.23,somari text,,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:02.44,somari text,,0,0,0,,感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:03.90,somari text,,0,0,0,,沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:06.36,somari text,,0,0,0,,我只是不想吃了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:09.86,somari text,,0,0,0,,烏佐伊你們是一起在旅行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.61,0:07:11.45,somari text,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.88,0:07:12.91,somari text,,0,0,0,,我們用馬車在旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:15.87,somari text,,0,0,0,,我們旅行是為了找藥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:18.45,somari text,,0,0,0,,我身體有點虛弱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:20.63,somari text,,0,0,0,,想要找治癒的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:25.21,somari text,,0,0,0,,她則是陪著無依無靠的我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.54,0:07:28.46,somari text,,0,0,0,,因為只有海特拉一個人太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:30.63,somari text,,0,0,0,,不過我們不是父女
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.30,0:07:33.55,somari text,,0,0,0,,我是高貴的哈耳庇厄一族
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.34,0:07:35.60,somari text,,0,0,0,,海特拉是法爾科荷魯一族
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.22,0:07:37.72,somari text,,0,0,0,,是長著鳥頭的種族
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:42.23,somari text,,0,0,0,,不過海特拉姑且也算我的監護人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:43.69,somari text,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.69,0:07:46.77,somari text,,0,0,0,,你們又是為什麼旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:49.61,somari text,,0,0,0,,你們的組合才奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:54.07,somari text,,0,0,0,,我們的旅途是為了找尋人類
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.53,0:07:56.16,somari text,,0,0,0,,人類？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.05,0:07:59.16,somari text,,0,0,0,,為什麼要找人類
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:02.79,somari text,,0,0,0,,為了調查  研究人類
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.85,0:08:08.17,somari text,,0,0,0,,我吃飽了  很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:10.34,somari text,,0,0,0,,烏佐伊人真好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.01,0:08:14.59,somari text,,0,0,0,,我說索瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:17.85,somari text,,0,0,0,,要穿越沙漠的話  要不要和我們一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:19.20,somari text,,0,0,0,,烏佐伊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.75,0:08:20.85,somari text,,0,0,0,,沒關係嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.14,0:08:23.44,somari text,,0,0,0,,穿越沙漠有很多沉重的行李
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:25.48,somari text,,0,0,0,,裝卸又很麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:27.46,somari text,,0,0,0,,真想有個幫手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:29.61,somari text,,0,0,0,,那是你的目的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:31.74,somari text,,0,0,0,,哎呀  暴露了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.60,0:08:34.95,somari text,,0,0,0,,不過讓你們白坐馬車的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:36.90,somari text,,0,0,0,,這也是個不錯的條件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.70,0:08:38.37,somari text,,0,0,0,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:41.49,somari text,,0,0,0,,烏佐伊讓我們坐她們的馬車誒  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.76,0:08:44.12,somari text,,0,0,0,,真的沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:47.54,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯  我沒關係…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.50,0:08:49.19,somari text,,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:52.60,somari text,,0,0,0,,那我和索瑪麗兩個人就承你們照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.15,0:08:54.30,somari text,,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.10,0:09:01.64,somari text,,0,0,0,,我好期待烏佐伊的馬車  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:02.68,somari text,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:17.20,somari text,,0,0,0,,烏佐伊  你想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:20.16,somari text,,0,0,0,,不是出於單純的熱心腸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.62,0:09:23.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.24,0:09:27.54,somari text,,0,0,0,,那孩子有和你一樣的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:29.67,somari text,,0,0,0,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.09,0:09:31.63,somari text,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.93,0:09:42.25,somari text,,0,0,0,,那孩子是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:45.81,somari text,,0,0,0,,和你一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:50.23,somari text,,0,0,0,,為什麼人類會和哥雷姆一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:53.59,somari text,,0,0,0,,這種事沒什麼所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:58.53,somari text,,0,0,0,,比起這個我有個主意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:00.32,somari text,,0,0,0,,主意？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:05.54,somari text,,0,0,0,,帶上那兩個人穿越沙漠的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.23,0:10:14.74,somari text,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:16.43,somari text,,0,0,0,,這樣做有什麼意義
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:24.01,somari text,,0,0,0,,海特拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.68,0:10:27.56,somari text,,0,0,0,,我們已經沒有時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.90,0:10:38.32,somari text,,0,0,0,,所以  拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:54.29,somari text,,0,0,0,,這是最後一件了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.06,0:10:55.96,somari text,,0,0,0,,謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.09,0:11:00.47,somari text,,0,0,0,,你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.48,0:11:07.81,somari text,,0,0,0,,把車輪換成撥沙車輪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.36,0:11:12.73,somari text,,0,0,0,,之後的路程如果不換成這種車輪的話馬車會陷到沙裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:14.44,somari text,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.36,0:11:16.52,somari text,,0,0,0,,好帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:19.86,somari text,,0,0,0,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.82,0:11:21.95,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.36,0:11:24.87,somari text,,0,0,0,,為什麼沙漠都是沙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.10,0:11:28.20,somari text,,0,0,0,,你真傻  因為都是沙才叫做沙漠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:29.37,somari text,,0,0,0,,這不是理所當然的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.77,0:11:32.32,somari text,,0,0,0,,那為什麼水…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.32,0:11:34.71,somari text,,0,0,0,,你好煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:38.21,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:40.87,somari text,,0,0,0,,發生什麼了嗎  海特拉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:43.76,somari text,,0,0,0,,不  沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:45.86,somari text,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:49.56,somari text,,0,0,0,,索瑪麗  出發的準備做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:50.90,somari text,,0,0,0,,要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:54.48,somari text,,0,0,0,,我有東西忘房間裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.44,0:11:57.62,somari text,,0,0,0,,沒辦法  去拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.62,0:12:01.34,somari text,,0,0,0,,離開房間時偷懶沒確認嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:05.70,somari text,,0,0,0,,烏佐伊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.58,0:12:09.63,somari text,,0,0,0,,我們先上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.67,0:12:29.24,somari text,,0,0,0,,雖然很熱但是感覺不到熱  風兒好涼快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.90,0:12:32.85,somari text,,0,0,0,,為了讓通風變得順暢我可是下了好大的功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.15,0:12:35.23,somari text,,0,0,0,,烏佐伊的馬車真是完美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.27,0:12:38.60,somari text,,0,0,0,,索瑪麗  進裡邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:41.57,somari text,,0,0,0,,沒事的  進裡邊的話就看不到外邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:47.91,somari text,,0,0,0,,我說烏佐伊  那個是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.74,0:12:50.83,somari text,,0,0,0,,那是仙人掌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:54.16,somari text,,0,0,0,,表皮很硬  但要是開花了就可以吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.93,0:12:55.96,somari text,,0,0,0,,好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.42,0:12:57.29,somari text,,0,0,0,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.90,0:13:00.74,somari text,,0,0,0,,取決於烹調方式吧  沒什麼特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.74,0:13:02.05,somari text,,0,0,0,,烏佐伊  那個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.24,0:13:03.72,somari text,,0,0,0,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:05.59,somari text,,0,0,0,,別人的話好好聽到最後…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.09,0:13:13.82,somari text,,0,0,0,,是沙塵暴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.22,0:13:15.25,somari text,,0,0,0,,大家小心一點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.76,0:13:22.67,somari text,,0,0,0,,氣流紊亂複雜  不像是沙漠倒像是波濤洶湧的大海
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:24.90,somari text,,0,0,0,,晃得好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:27.20,somari text,,0,0,0,,抓穩了可別掉下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:32.29,somari text,,0,0,0,,索瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:36.46,somari text,,0,0,0,,才說了怎麼你就是不聽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.58,0:13:39.75,somari text,,0,0,0,,你要是不在了就不好辦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.25,0:13:43.84,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:48.22,somari text,,0,0,0,,烏佐伊很珍視索瑪麗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:51.93,somari text,,0,0,0,,不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.01,0:13:55.57,somari text,,0,0,0,,那是什麼  有什麼東西正在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.06,0:14:02.90,somari text,,0,0,0,,是奧斯納沙漠裡兇殘的大魚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:04.69,somari text,,0,0,0,,沙鯊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.71,0:14:21.46,somari text,,0,0,0,,說不定還會追來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.04,0:14:23.36,somari text,,0,0,0,,趕快離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.08,0:14:27.26,somari text,,0,0,0,,好…好帥！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.42,0:14:29.40,somari text,,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.93,0:14:31.55,somari text,,0,0,0,,海特拉本來就帥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:35.06,somari text,,0,0,0,,索瑪麗的爸爸也很帥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.22,0:14:36.86,somari text,,0,0,0,,比不上海特拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.86,0:14:38.31,somari text,,0,0,0,,才沒這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.31,0:14:39.69,somari text,,0,0,0,,就是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.69,0:14:41.98,somari text,,0,0,0,,你們兩個就此打住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:42.55,somari text,,0,0,0,,氣溫下降了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:43.67,somari text,,0,0,0,,烏佐伊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.13,0:15:44.88,somari text,,0,0,0,,在做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.58,0:15:46.54,somari text,,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:48.75,somari text,,0,0,0,,礦石探測器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:51.34,somari text,,0,0,0,,裡邊的被稱之為「呼喚石」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.50,0:15:53.68,somari text,,0,0,0,,是在沙漠之中的洞穴裡採到的礦石
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:56.10,somari text,,0,0,0,,有在發出很小的聲音吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.31,0:16:02.02,somari text,,0,0,0,,真的誒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.45,0:16:07.06,somari text,,0,0,0,,有相同的石頭在附近的話它就會產生共鳴發出聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.87,0:16:12.51,somari text,,0,0,0,,也就是說  聲音越大的方向就會有洞穴是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:13.28,somari text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.99,0:16:17.07,somari text,,0,0,0,,那洞穴就是我們今天的營地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:27.88,somari text,,0,0,0,,好好聽的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.20,0:16:33.47,somari text,,0,0,0,,以前倒是覺得很吵人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.38,0:16:37.68,somari text,,0,0,0,,哈耳庇厄族的聽覺十分超常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.01,0:16:38.64,somari text,,0,0,0,,是到是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.41,0:16:41.72,somari text,,0,0,0,,什麼都能夠聽見也挺困擾的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.25,0:16:45.44,somari text,,0,0,0,,烏佐伊  我和哥雷姆先生來搭帳篷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.85,0:16:47.10,somari text,,0,0,0,,麻煩你準備一下燈光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.60,0:16:48.36,somari text,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.98,0:16:50.64,somari text,,0,0,0,,沒事做的話你也來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.82,0:16:58.24,somari text,,0,0,0,,為什麼要用籠子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.78,0:17:01.16,somari text,,0,0,0,,你真的是很多問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.85,0:17:03.87,somari text,,0,0,0,,閉上嘴跟著你就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:10.34,somari text,,0,0,0,,這個像是發光的石頭一樣的就是燈籠螢火蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.46,0:17:14.22,somari text,,0,0,0,,光亮正好合適  借來用一晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.42,0:17:16.72,somari text,,0,0,0,,索瑪麗也來抓抓看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.97,0:17:24.64,somari text,,0,0,0,,你這麼矮就抓一些矮處的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.69,0:17:28.40,somari text,,0,0,0,,就比如說藏在那黑色岩石附近的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:34.61,somari text,,0,0,0,,真的誒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.19,0:17:37.15,somari text,,0,0,0,,烏佐伊居然知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:39.66,somari text,,0,0,0,,是海特拉告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.49,0:17:44.04,somari text,,0,0,0,,險峻的山脈  森林的深處  寒冷的冰原
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.41,0:17:47.37,somari text,,0,0,0,,這些我們都一起去過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.17,0:17:50.79,somari text,,0,0,0,,索瑪麗和爸爸也去了很多的地方喲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:53.42,somari text,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.20,0:17:57.51,somari text,,0,0,0,,你和那個哥雷姆是什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.51,0:18:00.18,somari text,,0,0,0,,你們不是真正的父女吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.74,0:18:01.85,somari text,,0,0,0,,真正的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.80,0:18:05.81,somari text,,0,0,0,,索瑪麗的爸爸就是索瑪麗的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.40,0:18:07.81,somari text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.39,0:18:09.82,somari text,,0,0,0,,烏佐伊的爸爸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.11,0:18:12.27,somari text,,0,0,0,,我沒有父親
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.98,0:18:15.48,somari text,,0,0,0,,哈耳庇厄族由雌性所撫養長大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.89,0:18:17.15,somari text,,0,0,0,,只有母親
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.53,0:18:18.38,somari text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.74,0:18:20.62,somari text,,0,0,0,,那你媽媽在哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:24.08,somari text,,0,0,0,,聽海特拉說是因病去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.66,0:18:26.33,somari text,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.90,0:18:27.88,somari text,,0,0,0,,也沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.55,0:18:31.20,somari text,,0,0,0,,小時候的事情我也記不太清
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:39.55,somari text,,0,0,0,,海特拉一直陪在孑然一身的我的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:42.60,somari text,,0,0,0,,我喜歡海特拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.47,0:18:46.10,somari text,,0,0,0,,所以我不寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:48.60,somari text,,0,0,0,,和索瑪麗一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.74,0:18:50.49,somari text,,0,0,0,,什麼一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.67,0:18:53.46,somari text,,0,0,0,,烏佐伊你喜歡海特拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.73,0:18:55.61,somari text,,0,0,0,,索瑪麗喜歡爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:18:57.69,somari text,,0,0,0,,所以我們一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.70,0:19:02.24,somari text,,0,0,0,,別說話繼續幹活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.17,0:19:05.39,somari text,,0,0,0,,烏佐伊明明也在說話  不講道理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.39,0:19:06.45,somari text,,0,0,0,,手不要停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:08.45,somari text,,0,0,0,,燈籠螢火蟲就那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.37,0:19:10.50,somari text,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.59,0:19:17.27,somari text,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.59,0:19:19.92,somari text,,0,0,0,,為了海特拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:21.97,somari text,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.39,0:19:33.69,somari text,,0,0,0,,海特拉  我曾經聽聞過在沙漠西邊盡頭處有人類出現
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:35.83,somari text,,0,0,0,,你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.77,0:19:38.78,somari text,,0,0,0,,對不起  我什麼都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.17,0:19:40.63,somari text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:42.03,somari text,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:46.53,somari text,,0,0,0,,為什麼你在調查和尋找人類呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.45,0:19:48.12,somari text,,0,0,0,,是不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.81,0:19:51.79,somari text,,0,0,0,,和索瑪麗有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.20,0:19:55.79,somari text,,0,0,0,,詳細解釋十分困難
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.79,0:19:57.63,somari text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.90,0:19:59.09,somari text,,0,0,0,,我們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.81,0:20:00.55,somari text,,0,0,0,,回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.01,0:20:02.97,somari text,,0,0,0,,我們採回來了好多光光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.30,0:20:05.39,somari text,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:07.97,somari text,,0,0,0,,烏佐伊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.81,0:20:12.60,somari text,,0,0,0,,什麼都不用擔心  你好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:13.77,somari text,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.20,0:20:21.32,somari text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  還有什麼需要幫忙的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.07,0:20:22.74,somari text,,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.45,0:20:25.32,somari text,,0,0,0,,那我們去打一些水回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:27.20,somari text,,0,0,0,,深處裡應該有水
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:28.21,somari text,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.29,0:20:33.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,注意水邊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.37,0:20:34.58,somari text,,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:39.71,somari text,,0,0,0,,烏佐伊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:43.59,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.98,0:20:59.15,somari text,,0,0,0,,好奇怪啊烏佐伊  和來時的路不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.07,0:21:06.64,somari text,,0,0,0,,身體不舒服的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.64,0:21:07.41,somari text,,0,0,0,,哥雷姆先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.24,0:21:09.95,somari text,,0,0,0,,我開門見山地問了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:11.91,somari text,,0,0,0,,索瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:18.38,somari text,,0,0,0,,是人類吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:22.38,somari text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了  烏佐伊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.00,0:21:24.30,somari text,,0,0,0,,嚇壞我了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.30,0:21:26.38,somari text,,0,0,0,,為什麼你知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.59,0:21:27.47,somari text,,0,0,0,,請聽我說完
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.84,0:21:29.40,somari text,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.60,0:21:32.85,somari text,,0,0,0,,我也是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.50,0:21:35.56,somari text,,0,0,0,,你說你是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.23,0:21:40.73,somari text,,0,0,0,,我們為了治好這病踏上了旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.19,0:21:43.88,somari text,,0,0,0,,拜託了  我們一起…烏佐伊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.32,0:21:45.82,somari text,,0,0,0,,阻止她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.11,0:21:49.74,somari text,,0,0,0,,烏佐伊  我好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.45,0:21:51.58,somari text,,0,0,0,,別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.62,0:21:56.37,somari text,,0,0,0,,有了你的血  說不定海特拉就能得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.41,0:21:57.92,somari text,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.87,0:21:59.86,somari text,,0,0,0,,你的命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.96,0:22:04.09,somari text,,0,0,0,,我就收下了
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,somari text,,0,0,0,,——————ED——————
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.83,0:22:23.09,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}並ぶ影の大きさ比べ笑う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.83,0:22:23.09,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}比較著並排的影子相視而笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.47,0:22:26.66,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}夕暮れを背に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.47,0:22:26.66,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}把夕陽甩在身後
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.06,0:22:37.73,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}そっと風に乗せたのは　まだ小さな願い事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.06,0:22:37.73,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}乘風而去的是那小小的祈願
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.17,0:22:44.76,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}永遠とか　生命だとか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.17,0:22:44.76,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}什麼是永遠  什麼是生命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.08,0:22:49.36,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}何も分からずに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.08,0:22:49.36,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}我還一無所知
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.83,0:23:01.64,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}真っ直ぐな瞳で　見上げた横顔は眩しかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.83,0:23:01.64,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}只知道當我抬頭仰望你時  你的側臉總是那麼地閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.60,0:23:07.99,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}重ねた手に伝う温もりは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.60,0:23:07.99,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}手牽著手傳遞的這份溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.49,0:23:12.51,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}どんなときも愛をくれたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.49,0:23:12.51,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}無論何時都在給予我愛意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.89,0:23:18.40,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}溢れ出すこの想いが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.89,0:23:18.40,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}這不斷溢出的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.73,0:23:24.17,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}あなたに届く日まで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.73,0:23:24.17,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}直到傳達到給你的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.57,0:23:32.72,somari ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}交わした約束進もう  未来へ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.57,0:23:32.72,somari ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur10}向著共同許下的諾言和未來  前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.10,0:23:41.06,somari title,,0,0,0,,{\fade(1000,0)\blur5\pos(1536.8,1064.8)}生命之花仰望鳥兒
